# My Skill Library

## Paths

- **Library**: `~/my-skill-library/library` — where skill source directories live
- **Enabled**: `~/my-skill-library/enabled` — where symlinks go (Claude loads from here)
- **README**: `~/my-skill-library/README.md` — skill table auto-updated on create/remove

## Naming Convention

- **Prefix**: leave empty or set e.g. `nby-` for team skills
- **Format**: lowercase kebab-case

## Notes

Add any personal notes about your library setup here.
